00:18:13,263 --> 00:18:16,363
The only one who would mistake The Red Woman for Satoko,

310
00:18:16,363 --> 00:18:19,563
had to be the accomplice who carried out the trick.

311
00:18:19,563 --> 00:18:23,963
He was blabbering off in the bathroom back then

