00:19:02,863 --> 00:19:04,863
Then, who on earth?

326
00:19:04,863 --> 00:19:07,363
There's one likely person

327
00:19:07,363 --> 00:19:10,163
although deeply involved in this incident.

328
00:19:10,163 --> 00:19:13,663
No one knows whether she is dead or alive.

329
00:19:25,963 --> 00:19:27,463
I found you.

