That's it!

331
00:19:35,763 --> 00:19:38,663
There's no Red Woman here.

332
00:19:38,663 --> 00:19:43,263
Your revenge ended 15 years ago.

333
00:19:43,263 --> 00:19:47,363
Be quick to amend one's wrongs.

