00:19:47,363 --> 00:19:50,763
When a mistake is made be quick at making amends.

335
00:19:50,763 --> 00:19:54,063
There's no need for hesitation at all.

336
00:19:54,063 --> 00:19:55,863
We, the Nagano Prefectural Police Department

337
00:19:55,863 --> 00:19:57,763
